{"tid":151951,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 荷葉斑片蒸飯","createTime":"2017-03-11T10:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T01:30:37.000Z","uid":74981,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08b03c0c8b85a9a4c2e312c47c8f3a8c2c3d8bbf","tid":151951,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/009ad8da5d1d202a1d841046097c2475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F009ad8da5d1d202a1d841046097c2475.jpg&h=59212a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLINK如下, 有4 PARTS<br />\n<br />\nPart 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gz3VXLAiEig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgz3VXLAiEig&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=35e5c328\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gz3VXLAiEig</a><br />\n<br />\nPart 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nSwIu2O-P_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnSwIu2O-P_0&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=362fee5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nSwIu2O-P_0</a><br />\n<br />\nPart 3<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tBSmmraqObg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtBSmmraqObg&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=abe2527b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tBSmmraqObg</a><br />\n<br />\nPart 4<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kE8lgvK71Fk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkE8lgvK71Fk&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3714bdcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kE8lgvK71Fk</a><br />\n<br />\n步驟概述:<br />\n1. 煮飯 (1CUP米, 米水份量1比1)<br />\n2. 醃&quot;龍等&quot;, 鹽半茶匙,白胡椒粉少許, 生粉水少許<br />\n3. 荷葉熱水浸淋拎起備用<br />\n4. 蛋炒飯, 放荷葉上<br />\n5. 魚片走油, 7成油溫熄火浸, 過一陣再開中火泡一陣, 5成熟撈起鋪飯面<br />\n6. 加熟蒜在魚片上, 用荷葉包番埋<br />\n7. 水滾大火煎4分鐘<br />\n8. 爆少少蔥油, 淋係魚面, 完成.<br />\n9. 蒸既時間因應魚片既厚度而唔同,大家靈活變通 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b2fd78f01f1329afef2477dd01714cbdcd16ae","tid":151951,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:22:03.000Z","msg":"廚房佬去賣燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩玩法"},{"pid":"81cefa0aec1d7f3bf9ef502493a1f5fef5e43366","tid":151951,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廚房佬去賣燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b3b5b9352f07bbe3b4f61bfd152e6274838703","tid":151951,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"睇圖覺得好腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc147bd710f2c2fbaa9d49bf55e4bf9f5333d6c","tid":151951,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇圖覺得好腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔腥架，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed32203ca7ad80d8dcaa9823892a025d8189c115","tid":151951,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"幾時出你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adfe2eeaebb628b02ee151d4e82f1ec0b23878f","tid":151951,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"剪下片好&hellip;<br />\npart1 13:00"},{"pid":"4d16749642e60421eb4643886b890b342609cb90","tid":151951,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剪下片好&hellip;<br />\npart1 13:00</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b750c69d37